snippet.title: Zombie Parking - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
Zombie Parking - computer indie-game in the genre of third-person shooter and survival horror. The game is developed on Unreal Engine 4 for Windows, Mac, Linux platforms.

The goal of the game is to hold out as long as possible beating attacks of the living dead, who become stronger, faster and more dangerous with each killed enemy.

Developed by XPAGAME

#steam #steamgames #steamgame #xpagame #zombies #zombie #zombieparking #unrealengine4 #unrealengine

FUN FACT: To quote my Steam review: "If Left 4 Dead was developed by fermented sea cucumbers, Zombie Parking is the result."
